high_descs: Go a bit to the right to the counter between the stove and the sink.
Pick up a butterknife from the counter.
Go towards the lemon.
Slice up the nearby lemon next to the sink.
Place the butterknife down on the counter next to the spray bottle.
Pick up a slice of lemon from the plate.
Turn right towards the fridge.
Place the lemon slice into the fridge, let it cool, then remove the lemon.
Turn back towards the sink and counters.
Place the lemon down on the sink next to the stove.
anns.task_desc: Slice a Lemon, cool down a slice in the fridge, and place it on a Sink.

high_descs: Turn left to face the smaller sink.
Pick up the butterknife from the smaller sink.
Turn left to head to the larger lemon sink.
Slice the lemon in the smaller sink with the knife.
Put the butterknife on the kitchen counter.
Pick up a slice of lemon from the smaller sink.
Turn right to face the fridge.
Cool the lemon slice in the fridge and pull it out.
Turn around to walk up to the larger sink.
Put the lemon slice on the kitchen counter.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold lemon on the sink.

high_descs: Face the sink in the kitchen.
Pick up the butterknife from the counter
Walk over to the left side of the kitchen sink and place the lemon there.
Cut the lemon in the sink.
Set the butterknife down on the sink.
Pick up the lemon from the sink.
Walk over to the fridge.
Place the lemon piece into the fridge then remove the lemon piece again.
Walk over to the left side of the kitchen sink.
Set the lemon piece down on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cut and cool the Lemon then put it on the Sink
